    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolute mint condition. No scratches, no smells, just pure driving bliss. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S), featuring the sophisticated 13B-REW twin-rotor powerplant. This example retains its original sequential twin-turbocharger architecture, delivering a linear power band with a seamless transition at 4,500 RPM. Mechanical highlights include a documented high-compression test, a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential, and a perfectly preserved four-wheel double-wishbone suspension system. The chassis rigidity is uncompromising, and the vacuum-controlled solenoid rack has been serviced to ensure peak boost response. Unmodified and structurally flawless, this FD represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM performance engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
