    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster and zero road rash. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom aroma; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance and exclusively original parts. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule experience for the discerning driver who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
