      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, drives like a dream, and is ready for a new home. You won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
